title: WTF | Watch: Man not at all freaked out when testing new Telsa self-driving car in traffic
text:
The future is here. And it's driving itself. And of course the man's freaked. He's freaked witless. Imagine a control freak taking this amazing piece of machinery for a test drive? Wouldn't happen.
Jalopnik took Tesla's Model S Level 2 autonomous system, known as Autopilot, for a spin. They summed the experience up in four words, those being "super fun" and "super weird". The video, which was uploaded to YouTube today, already has over a million views, and you'll see why...
